
Boot Strap Visual Breakpoints:
Extra-small devices(phones) -  xs -  Less Than 768px(<768px)
Small devices(tablets)  - sm  >= 768px
Medium devices(desktops)- md -  >= 992 px
Large devices(desktops)-  lg - >= 1200px

Example:
<div class="container">  // you can use "container-fluid" for fluid layour while resizing your browser.
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-sm-12">
      <! put your content here !>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

* Meta tag must be added in the head section of the page for acheive the responsiveness in mobile devices.
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
